description:
A mysterious masked woman working under Ulyte`s wing with an unknown agenda. She briefly joined Lashara`s platoon after the Head Church`s headquarters was destroyed by Doll, but she later shows her true colors at the Barrier Workshop while holding a mysterious object in her hands. Her Seikijin is grey with a cape and a mask with active camouflage armed with a large sniper rifle.
Source: Wiki
name: Neizai Wan
